text: Input/Output Data The input/output data is the type of data that an agent expects to receive and delivers. The agent expects and delivers data in bytearray format. MIM The Encryptor agent does not have any agent specific MIM parameters. For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM parameters, see Administration and Management .
